{"tid":2495093,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家同林家謙道歉","createTime":"2021-04-19T03:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T04:00:54.000Z","uid":321895,"like":13,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"283ac5660cfe91d8bf494a1224fe2705545ff7f0","tid":2495093,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:46:50.000Z","msg":"由林家謙14年開始，佢寫左超多隻好歌，當年完全無人留言佢個名，咁樣對佢公平咩？<br />\n<br />\n呢到Highlight幾首<br />\n2015 矛盾一生<br />\n2016 多少年、自由飛翔、小故事<br />\n2017 原來只因深愛著、紅線<br />\n2018 心之科學、伯利恆的主角、感激遇到你<br />\n2019 下一位前度、平安夜、原罪<br />\n2020 拼命無恙、一人之境、我心中尚未崩壞的部分<br />\n<br />\n家謙由一開始出嚟唱歌就已經好謙虛<br />\n作為一個幕後人 佢真係唔識對鏡頭講野<br />\n<br />\n大家可以睇下佢初初上chillclub既表演<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/V_MaQDJLDx4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FV_MaQDJLDx4&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=ee32ac20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/V_MaQDJLDx4</a><br />\n<br />\n覺得佢係藍絲既 可以聽埋呢首歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n_VwZ9r28Fk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn_VwZ9r28Fk&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=e71c581d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n_VwZ9r28Fk</a><br />\n<br />\n還有.... 佢既心聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pbfL_FqEmuE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpbfL_FqEmuE&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=2893b091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pbfL_FqEmuE</a><br />\n<br />\n希望連登仔可以同家謙道歉<br />\n可以唔識欣賞別人既作品<br />\n但請尊重為本地文化出力既每一位<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">家謙<br />\n期待你唱多啲好歌呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV8aQCbvtegfF7kEx6vbd3F7Y88fuaYDXWcTL87MM6BU6?filename=aweeQ46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaweeQ46.png&h=09adaf75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ea245a1c9e14384fab2e1b7611324bb0ba3c437","tid":2495093,"uid":321895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d97315ffef4cadc2efe9eead9ce9114c37fc29f1","tid":2495093,"uid":321895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:49:15.000Z","msg":"你班連衛乒除左識批鬥仲識咩"},{"pid":"bcb6cf47fd36724bf57b354f027fa823af5e0d11","tid":2495093,"uid":321895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7b5ea298fab61371aad145f0d2d0e4b0663f68b","tid":2495093,"uid":321895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:49:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b1f2f6d2ec7f37f0ce0148061ce0e742b258106","tid":2495093,"uid":321895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:49:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab30238c9638dce1e6a4063de53572405b171d49","tid":2495093,"uid":321895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:50:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c619b659f14e8b7bb75c873f680fe55d8b984b36","tid":2495093,"uid":321895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:50:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2ea7dc538dfee48709ea6e0c44a1db49b86973e","tid":2495093,"uid":321895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"daf59897221b0ba0b74c7a27b0a9ffc289c07dcb","tid":2495093,"uid":321895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81c1ff329227ef0ead2127a6691b9d654241c82e","tid":2495093,"uid":140583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:52:37.000Z","msg":"Eason 都大把歌好似好黃咁啦，最後咪又係奶"},{"pid":"31dc88406e750650e8446d3b83fb334bad207a93","tid":2495093,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81c1ff329227ef0ead2127a6691b9d654241c82e","tid":2495093,"uid":140583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:52:37.000Z","msg":"Eason 都大把歌好似好黃咁啦，最後咪又係奶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:57:05.000Z",